{"tid":1290610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我知今日大家都好唔想走，但仲有聽日啊！要留力！","createTime":"2019-07-06T14:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T16:36:15.000Z","uid":106093,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9b2b17d375fef2b78381efec338446d57c88fed8","tid":1290610,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"發夢睇住班狗衝入黎，推開所有人 包括記者<br />\n捉左隻鬼出黎<br />\n由於衝得太突然，有人見到有手足俾人拉左<br />\n最後有議員問班狗<br />\n話班狗話無拉到任何請願人士<br />\n當然無人信 個個都好想留 好明白<br />\n<br />\n但今次真係太少人，一清場就玩完<br />\n我睇到好多手足 有唔同意見<br />\n但希望下次大家真係可以冷靜<br />\n分析下現場局勢先<br />\n唔想手足送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">留力！聽日！</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個夢睇到香港執法者係幾咁仆街<br />\n大家都唔想見到手足俾人拉<br />\n要走一齊走！！"},{"pid":"6543f1bc605c0a46f9d64d981bf0e469021a3018","tid":1290610,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"fe7ec2670bf699d9df073c5428200b2803306435","tid":1290610,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"783d417a98b4f5bca1a98bbfbec07f39a5732f46","tid":1290610,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"a14e4137d7577cbf7274d1d33ce083e5c7a4f6d2","tid":1290610,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"30799aea7645abc6b26f386026ec48ed54c26779","tid":1290610,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:25:07.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"aefd1d9c87f8305f177d89a5de1fa529b8bf027b","tid":1290610,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"05909af8e9dbf9db8aa3259953f5d20ac58be1a6","tid":1290610,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:25:56.000Z","msg